    "## ✅ **10. أفضل الممارسات (Best Practices)** ⭐ محدث\n",
    "\n",
    "### **10.1 قواعد XAML**\n",
    "\n",
    "```xml\n",
    "<!-- ✅ استخدام Border بدلاً من Frame -->\n",
    "<Border StrokeShape=\"RoundRectangle 12\"\n",
    "        BackgroundColor=\"White\"\n",
    "        Padding=\"16\">\n",
    "    <Label Text=\"محتوى\" />\n",
    "</Border>\n",
    "\n",
    "<!-- ✅ للقوائم المنسدلة المخصصة: استخدم CollectionView مع TapGestureRecognizer -->\n",
    "<Border BackgroundColor=\"White\" StrokeShape=\"RoundRectangle 12\">\n",
    "    <Grid>\n",
    "        <Label Text=\"{Binding SelectedItem.NameAr}\" />\n",
    "        <Label Text=\"▼\" HorizontalOptions=\"End\" />\n",
    "    </Grid>\n",
    "    <Border.GestureRecognizers>\n",
    "        <TapGestureRecognizer Command=\"{Binding ToggleListCommand}\" />\n",
    "    </Border.GestureRecognizers>\n",
    "</Border>\n",
    "\n",
    "<!-- ✅ ActivityIndicator للتحميل -->\n",
    "<ActivityIndicator IsRunning=\"{Binding IsBusy}\" \n",
    "                   IsVisible=\"{Binding IsBusy}\"\n",
    "                   Color=\"#1B5A7A\" />\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### **10.2 قواعد C#**\n",
    "\n",
    "```csharp\n",
    "// ✅ التحقق من null في الـ Command (وليس في XAML)\n",
    "ToggleCityListCommand = new Command(() => \n",
    "{\n",
    "    if (SelectedCountry != null)  // التحقق هنا\n",
    "        ShowCityList = !ShowCityList;\n",
    "});\n",
    "\n",
    "// ✅ استخدام IsBusy للتحميل\n",
    "try\n",
    "{\n",
    "    IsBusy = true;\n",
    "    var data = await _apiService.GetAsync<List<MyDto>>(\"api/endpoint\");\n",
    "}\n",
    "finally\n",
    "{\n",
    "    IsBusy = false;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// ✅ التحقق من null قبل التكرار\n",
    "if (countries != null)\n",
    "{\n",
    "    foreach (var c in countries)\n",
    "    {\n",
    "        // ...\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### **10.3 قواعد جديدة من التجربة**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **للأندرويد الحقيقي:** استخدم IP الجهاز بدلاً من `localhost` في `ApiService`\n",
    "2. **للأداء:** أضف `Timeout` للـ HttpClient (30 ثانية كافية)\n",
    "3. **للتوسع:** أنشئ `BaseViewModel` يحوي `IsBusy` و `ApiService`\n",
    "4. **للاختبار السريع:** أنشئ Postman Collection لجميع الـ APIs\n",
    "\n",
